description: ICICI Prudential Mutual Fund - Bharat 22 ETF is an exchange traded fund co-launched by ICICI Bank Ltd. and Prudential plc. It is managed by ICICI Prudential Asset Management Company Limited. The fund invests in the public equity markets of India. It seeks to invest in the stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund invests in the stocks of large-cap companies. It seeks to replicate the performance of the S&P BSE Bharat 22 Index, by investing in the stocks of companies as per their weightings in the index. ICICI Prudential Mutual Fund - Bharat 22 ETF was formed on November 24, 2017 and is domiciled in India.
name: BHARAT 22 ETF
